<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3250402">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3250402/" class="title-link">读史记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3250402"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/29295323/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/29295323/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Jenna</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-05-08"
      class="main-meta">2010-05-08 14:14:39</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3250402_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  以前买过一本史记的译本，原版看不懂！当然有了王立群对史记的解读，是我对历史有了更深一步的了解~此本是上册，特别好看的一本书，从荆轲刺秦王开始讲起，清楚的讲述了秦国这样一个庞大的帝国是怎么样缔造的，秦始皇又是怎样一位风云人物，深藏众多秘密。  很赞同这样几句话：...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_3250402_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_3250402_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7478192">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7478192/" class="title-link">秦Inc 并购记</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7478192"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/bdleizi/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u42844970-290.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/bdleizi/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">姜小白</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-05-21"
      class="main-meta">2015-05-21 10:49:12</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7478192_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  看战国七雄争霸，秦国胜出，靠啥呢？得人才者得天下，是这样吗？韩非比商鞅怎么样，有过之而无不及吧，韩非可是嬴政的偶像呢。但是商鞅把秦国打造成一个虎狼之国，引三晋之农补秦地广人稀使其经济基础厚实，再给平民上升阶梯杀敌即可得爵位，使秦国战斗力也同样彪悍。而韩非呢...

